text: Blue Beetle is a 2023 American superhero movie based on the DC Comics character Jaime Reyes / Blue Beetle. It was released by Warner Bros. Pictures. It is the 16th movie in the DC Extended Universe (DCEU). The movie is directed by Angel Manuel Soto and stars Xolo Maridueña as the title character. == Cast == * Xolo Maridueña as Jaime Reyes / Blue Beetle * Bruna Marquezine as Penny * Belissa Escobedo as Milagros Reyes * George Lopez as Rudy * Adriana Barraza as Nana * Elpidia Carrillo as Rocio Reyes * Damián Alcázar as Alberto Reyes * Raoul Trujillo as Ignacio Carapax / OMAC: * Susan Sarandon as Victoria Kord Harvey Guillén stars Dr. "Sanchez", a scientist who works for Victoria; and Becky G as the voice of Khaji-Da, an entity that imbues and controls the Scarab. An uncredited actor portrays Ted Kord in a voice-only cameo appearance in the mid-credits scene. ==References== Category:DC Extended Universe movies Category:American superhero movies
